title: Citrix XenApp Controller: Overall State
agents: windows
catalog: app/citrix
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the state of Citrix XenApp 7.x controllers.
 The citrix_farm.ps1 plugin must be installed on the controller, and
 the Checkmk agent must be executed with Citrix Admin permissions
 for this to work. The check reports OK if and only if the controller
 state is Active.

discovery:
 One service is created for each controller.
